title: ComboUpdate - 10.5.3 plus software for Mac OS X-Leopard
description:
Combined Update Mac-OS-X Leopard version 10.5.3
Adapted for motherboards series: P5LVM - 1394 graphics cards using NVidia - 5,6,7 and 8 series (driver - NVinject -0.2.1), as well as in audio updates (driver - ALC883)
You can use on other motherboards but tentatively prepare
their video and audio driver to replace instead above
Should set the following "mother":
P5L-1394, P5LD-2SE, P5LD-2, P5GCMX-1333, and in the other series only experimentally?

P.S. I apologize for bad translation into English ...
